Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.08,0:01:34.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在身处天神峠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算是熬过了缆车和登山吊椅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.59,0:01:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷川岳的登山终于正式开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.05,0:01:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,景色绝佳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.30,0:01:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 危险啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.26,0:01:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到这个天神峠我们已经爬了1500米了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.23,0:01:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷川岳是1977米 我们要去那里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.52,0:01:56.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷川岳的两个山顶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.94,0:01:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫做TOMA之耳 和OKI之耳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.74,0:02:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着好可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.11,0:02:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说是因为这两个山顶很像是猫耳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.91,0:02:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才起了这样的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.70,0:02:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.58,0:02:14.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是TOMA是山的入口 OKI是里面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:17.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山中小屋叫做肩之屋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肩？猫有肩膀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.34,0:02:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到猫咪的肩膀那里要沿着山脊走过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.14,0:02:26.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和日向的约定很快就要实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.64,0:02:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再一次在那座山上看日出的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.48,0:02:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(1088,607)}「成为朋友？」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.11,0:02:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在山上吃的饭最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.45,0:02:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得好好摄取能量哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:02:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 刚才谢谢你帮我捡票
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.71,0:03:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.46,0:03:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是缆车搭乘处的那个孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请保佑我平安登顶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请保佑我能够看到美丽的日出
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.14,0:03:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请保佑世界和平
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.85,0:03:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请保佑我能见到小群马
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.45,0:03:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是下坡路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.95,0:03:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比爬坡轻松 多好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.12,0:03:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下坡的话还得把下坡的部分再爬回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.54,0:03:38.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富士山一开始很轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不能大意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花儿好漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.30,0:03:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有蝉声还有蜻蜓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.38,0:03:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有蝴蝶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不知道是什么季节了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到山顶为止还有3.3公里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.85,0:03:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光看数字的话好近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:04:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪啊 是不是比刚才增加了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.73,0:04:03.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种小事就不要在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.07,0:04:07.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 日向 枫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实今天是心夏的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.12,0:04:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢 到了山中小屋…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.95,0:04:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.83,0:04:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.71,0:04:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.17,0:04:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.59,0:04:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.47,0:04:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前面很难走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然很难走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 变艰难了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这点小事可难不倒我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.03,0:04:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种路真亏我们小时候能爬上来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为小时候身子轻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.53,0:04:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟富士山比起来 这算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:02.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.38,0:05:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:09.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.97,0:05:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,点心 点心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.64,0:05:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是一个人来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:21.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熊穴泽 有熊先生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.69,0:05:23.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羊羹好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又吃羊羹？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.94,0:05:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是老爷爷么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.36,0:05:27.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先走一步哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏 我在上面等你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.93,0:05:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是从哪里来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.56,0:06:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我是从琦玉的饭能来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:12.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…是群马的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍子好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高崎来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.49,0:06:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我今天来的时候坐电车路过了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.87,0:06:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.33,0:06:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 我说了什么话惹她生气了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以跟着她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越来越远了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.43,0:06:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个孩子不会察言观色吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.82,0:06:57.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天狗的滞留处？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.58,0:07:04.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是第一次到这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.00,0:07:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来拍过好几次照片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要拍这种景色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.18,0:07:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要长时间待在喜欢的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.68,0:07:20.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就走得快了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍了什么样的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是以前拍的谷川岳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.23,0:07:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想再看见这样的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.11,0:07:37.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了随时都能看得见 一直放在相机里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.37,0:07:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要爬山呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:48.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因 因为开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.21,0:07:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 我是来看日出的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.30,0:07:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是和朋友的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.01,0:08:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经几次留宿在山上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是清晨没有放晴也很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.89,0:08:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会出雾 不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.81,0:08:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能看见就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.69,0:08:12.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.69,0:08:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫穂香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫葵 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:19.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.28,0:08:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,景色真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.95,0:08:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉自己都变成了天狗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她叫做穗香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:30.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教 我叫日向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.33,0:08:31.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是枫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.29,0:08:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是心夏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.88,0:08:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.09,0:08:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穗香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穗香也要留宿山中小屋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.81,0:08:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话 一起吃晚饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.15,0:08:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她好像是不喜欢与人交往的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.94,0:08:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 说不定不是那样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.41,0:09:07.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云的走向很奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪日向说希望下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的错吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是忏悔岩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.71,0:09:20.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天神大人也会在这里忏悔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.97,0:09:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.55,0:09:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿上雨衣比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.77,0:09:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包也不要忘了用雨具遮挡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.60,0:09:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对是日向的错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.73,0:09:35.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有言灵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.65,0:09:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连心夏也这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向也忏悔下比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.36,0:09:43.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我这是向谁道歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.91,0:09:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到山中小屋还有一点点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心脚下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.16,0:09:51.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.71,0:09:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈给我买的鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.00,0:09:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走起来好轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.71,0:10:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨衣好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.42,0:10:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通气性也很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 雨衣确实很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枫 真的谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.73,0:10:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好能帮到你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.06,0:10:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这钟我也有印象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.75,0:10:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进去休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.30,0:10:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大雨天真是辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.93,0:10:51.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请在晚餐准备好之前休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.35,0:10:54.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.31,0:10:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡觉请用上面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.23,0:11:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雨了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.82,0:11:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 葵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.66,0:11:14.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.59,0:11:22.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
